<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Account Access Restored</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .success-box {
            background: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>âœ… Account Access Restored</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= name %>!</h2>

            <div class="success-box">
                <h3>Great news! Your Finder App account access has been restored.</h3>
            </div>

            <p>Your account suspension has been lifted and you can now access all Finder App features again.</p>

            <h3>What you can do now:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Log into your account</li>
                <li>Access your profile and settings</li>
                <li>Use all Finder App services</li>
                <li>Connect with the community</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= process.env.BETTER_AUTH_URL || 'http://localhost:3000' %>" class="button">
                    Access Your Account
                </a>
            </div>

            <h3>Moving Forward:</h3>
            <p>We encourage you to review our community guidelines to ensure a positive experience for everyone on the
                platform.</p>

            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help.</p>

            <p>Welcome back to Finder App!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Finder Team</p>
            <p>Thank you for being part of our community.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>